span.span: Defines and creates generic type parameters for dynamically defined generic types and methods.

summary.span: 這個類別無法被繼承。

remarks.format: ## Remarks 您可以取得陣列所使用的物件方法來加入型別參數，動態型別，因此讓它成為泛型型別，或使用將動態方法的型別參數的方法。You can get an array of objects by using the method to add type parameters to a dynamic type, thus making it a generic type, or by using the method to add type parameters to a dynamic method. 使用新增至類型參數條件約束的物件。Use the objects to add constraints to the type parameters. 條件約束有三種：Constraints are of three kinds: - 基底類型條件約束會指定指派給泛型類型參數的任何型別必須衍生自特定的基底型別。The base type constraint specifies that any type assigned to the generic type parameter must derive from a particular base type. 藉由設定這個條件約束方法。Set this constraint by using the method. - 介面條件約束會指定任何指派給泛型類型參數的類型必須實作特定介面。An interface constraint specifies that any type assigned to the generic type parameter must implement a particular interface. 使用設定介面條件約束方法。Set the interface constraints by using the method. - 特殊條件約束會指定任何指派給泛型類型參數的類型必須有預設建構函式，必須是參考類型，或必須是實值型別。Special constraints specify that any type assigned to the generic type parameter must have a default constructor, must be a reference type, or must be a value type. 使用設定類型參數特殊條件約束方法。Set the special constraints for a type parameter by using the method. 介面條件約束和特殊條件約束無法使用擷取的方法類別。Interface constraints and special constraints cannot be retrieved using methods of the class. 當您建立包含的型別參數的泛型型別之後時，您可以使用其以反映條件約束的物件。Once you have created the generic type that contains the type parameters, you can use its object to reflect the constraints. 使用方法來取得型別參數，並針對每個類型參數使用方法來取得基底類型條件約束和介面條件約束和屬性來取得特殊條件約束。Use the method to get the type parameters, and for each type parameter use the method to get the base type constraint and interface constraints, and the property to get the special constraints. ## Examples 下列程式碼範例會使用兩個類型參數，建立泛型型別，並將其儲存 GenericEmitExample1.dll 的組件。The following code example creates a generic type with two type parameters, and saves them in the assembly GenericEmitExample1.dll. 您可以使用[Ildasm.exe （IL 反組譯工具）](~/docs/framework/tools/ildasm-exe-il-disassembler.md)若要檢視產生的型別。You can use the [Ildasm.exe (IL Disassembler)](~/docs/framework/tools/ildasm-exe-il-disassembler.md) to view the generated types. 定義動態的泛型型別所需的步驟的更詳細說明，請參閱 < [ 如何： 定義泛型類型使用反映發出](~/docs/framework/reflection-and-codedom/how-to-define-a-generic-type-with-reflection-emit.md)。For a more detailed explanation of the steps involved in defining a dynamic generic type, see [How to: Define a Generic Type with Reflection Emit](~/docs/framework/reflection-and-codedom/how-to-define-a-generic-type-with-reflection-emit.md).
